    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>One Hand Clapping 是一款声乐 2D 平台游戏。通过对着麦克风唱歌或哼唱来解决难题，并在改变周围世界时对自己声音的力量充满信心。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893720/extras/dc8a3079de8496168c66f199d9d0f1fd.poster.avif?t=1770374700\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893720/extras/dc8a3079de8496168c66f199d9d0f1fd.webm?t=1770374700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893720/extras/dc8a3079de8496168c66f199d9d0f1fd.mp4?t=1770374700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One Hand Clapping 是一款轻松、鼓舞人心的拼图平台游戏，专注于声音输入，以在充满活力的世界中取得进步。当您使用旋律、节奏和和声作为工具时，建立对您声音的信心。慢慢来。你没有什么可失去的，也不会因为犯错而受到惩罚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识可爱的角色，他们将为您提供帮助，为您加油，并激发自我表达而不会咄咄逼人。您不必是歌手天才也能享受单手鼓掌。只需克服您的疑虑，与沉默作斗争，并唱出您的歌曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893720/extras/68742a138a3abcaea145747cf92e5a25.poster.avif?t=1770374700\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893720/extras/68742a138a3abcaea145747cf92e5a25.webm?t=1770374700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893720/extras/68742a138a3abcaea145747cf92e5a25.mp4?t=1770374700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>只需连接一个麦克风，你就可以开始了！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 用你的声音解决谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在六个广阔、充满活力的生物群落中玩耍</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 唱歌、哼唱和节拍器来改变世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 认识三位异想天开的隐士，他们会在整个音乐之旅中帮助你</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 增强对你声音的信心</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 唱你的歌</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893720/extras/e3e8516069db41d9fcb388efb1f9734e.poster.avif?t=1770374700\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/893720/extras/e3e8516069db41d9fcb388efb1f9734e.webm?t=1770374700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
